*Prezime* je ime porodice. (The surname is the family name.)

Moje *prezime* je Petrović. (My surname is Petrović.)

*Prezimena* pomažu u identifikaciji ljudi. (Surnames help in the identification of people.)

On je promenio svoje *prezime*. (He changed his surname.)

Ona je ubacila svoje *prezime* u bazu podataka. (She entered her surname in the database.)